  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The second, our obligation is to talk about this as long as we live, to tell the world that inhumanity man to man is the biggest crime ever committed.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Humanity man to man is show compassion, love, and respect to another human being.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we have to talk about this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And because I live thanks to the humanity of a man who was a German Catholic, bon vivant, womanizer, part of an espionage organization who gambled [NON-ENGLISH] with his life, and his money, and his wife's life, and he succeed-- proved the point that humanity still exists.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And because exist, we have to develop and teach the young people how to love and respect.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Instead, what is much easier because a child is born with a love to mother, and to family, and to-- to surrounding condition.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Hatred is accumulated through a connection with people who brainwashed them, or implemented negative aspect towards other people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this is what I decide to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The minute I was liberated, the minute I came to-- to Munich, the minute I came to New York, the minute I came to Los Angeles, never stop talking about this.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Many times I had, when I came to Jewish federation that we want to organize survivor organization, and we would like to make a Yom Hashoah in 1953.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They said, forget it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You are in America.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You will have to remember, you are starting brand new.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I said, when we forget it, we are all doomed to perish again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We can never forget it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
